powerpc/asm: Add some opcodes in asm/ppc-opcode.h for PPC32 eBPF

The following opcodes will be needed for the implementation
of eBPF for PPC32. Add them in asm/ppc-opcode.h

PPC_RAW_ADDE
PPC_RAW_ADDZE
PPC_RAW_ADDME
PPC_RAW_MFLR
PPC_RAW_ADDIC
PPC_RAW_ADDIC_DOT
PPC_RAW_SUBFC
PPC_RAW_SUBFE
PPC_RAW_SUBFIC
PPC_RAW_SUBFZE
PPC_RAW_ANDIS
PPC_RAW_NOR

